-- Lehman Will Allow $6.6 Billion in Claims by German Affiliate Bankhaus
-- B y   L i n d a   S a n d l e r
-- 2011-02-03T18:33:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-03/lehman-to-allow-6-6-billion-in-claims-by-bankrupt-affiliate-in-germany.html
  Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc . said it
would allow its bankrupt German affiliate, Lehman Brothers
Bankhaus AG, to claim $6.6 billion from its parent as part of a
settlement of “relationships” between the two companies,
according to a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
